document_data.mainbody:
iren StreetThe FR Interactive Atlas map of Waterdeep names this as "Starn Street" but the zoomed in section of the same map lists it as Siren Street. was a small road that was located in the city of Waterdeep.
Siren Street was located in Waterdeeps Dock Ward. It branched south off of Ship Street one building south of the intersection with Odd Street, passing through a block of buildings south and west to end on Dock Street on the waterfront.
* Helmstar Warehouse
